data.description: Charming Downtown Delray Beach Single Family Home, Discover Ideal Coastal Living. Welcome to your delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom single family home in the heart of downtown Delray Beach. Nestled on a spacious 6,651 square foot lot, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, beachside living and everything Delray has to offer. This lot offers ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even future expansion. The property features and elongated driveway with room for 4+ cars. Once you step through your spacious outdoor patio and into the home you will be greeted with an abundance of natural light, updated bathroom, kitchen with modern appliances, and split floor plan. The Property is located in an Opportunity Zone AND within the Delray Beach CRA district! Situated less than a mile to the Pristine Beaches, & just two blocks south of Swinton Avenue, and three blocks east of Atlantic Avenue. This home is conveniently located near the exciting Sundy Village Development, which promises to be a hub of entertainment, dining, and community events. Be part of the growing cultural scene in downtown Delray Beach. Delray Beach is known for its vibrant arts scene, upscale shopping, and a wide array of dining options. Whether you're seeking a permanent residence or a vacation getaway, this home offers the perfect blend of location, convenience, and potential.
